<p>Nesse pequeno pseudoc√≥digo, caso a condi√ß√£o seja <strong>T</strong><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">(true)</code> √© executada a <strong>opera√ß√£o 1</strong>, caso contr√°rio √© 
